    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Rare find alert \u2014 this car is in absolutely mint condition! If you've been searching for a used car that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, your search is over. Every surface, every system, and every detail has been impeccably maintained \u2014 there's simply no meaningful wear to report. This is as close to a brand-new experience as you'll find in the used car market, and it shows the moment you lay eyes on it. Don't miss your chance to own something truly special!",
