    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in fair condition, and we want buyers to have a realistic picture before reaching out. The exterior shows visible wear \u2014 you can expect some scratches, minor dents, and surface blemishes consistent with everyday use over the years. The paint has lost some of its luster in places, and there may be small rust spots or chips that are noticeable up close. The interior is functional but shows its age: expect worn upholstery, some scuffs on trim panels, and general signs of regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some maintenance attention \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting into. All major systems are operational, but this is not a pristine vehicle. What you're getting is a car that can serve as reliable daily transportation with some investment of care, priced honestly to reflect its true condition. No surprises \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
      "price": 15500.0,
